ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v26.message

Class EAC_U07

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v26.message.EAC_U07
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class EAC_U07
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a EAC_U07 message structure (see chapter 13.3.7). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (Message Header)
    • 2: SFT (Software Segment) optional repeating
    • 3: UAC (User Authentication Credential Segment) optional
    • 4: EQU (Equipment Detail)
    • 5: EAC_U07_COMMAND (a Group object) repeating
    • 6: ROL (Role) optional
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
